snippet.textDisplay:
these forecasts are useless because we have no idea the true infection rate in China.... inability to test + many people don't test/self-quarantine + many people never develop symptoms beyond mild so never report it. moreover, much of the spread was pre-quarantine pre-awareness. if you applied the Wuhan mortality rates to US, annualized per capita, it would be nearly half a million dead (flu is about 60K a year). but if you apply post-quarantine rates in Beijing, it would be much less severe than the flu. moreover, we have no idea the true mortality rate because we don't know how many reports go unreported .... TBH we won't truly know until COVID is in an entirely post-quarantine post-awareness sample with very proactive rates of testing -- e.g. Korea or Japan maybe.

Iran data I would imagine must be far far worse than they're reporting. not just 1 but 2 Canadians (two!) catch it while visiting Iran... and the Health Minister got it.... what are the chances those 3 people all know the same 20-30 cases (over 1-2 weeks ago when they caught it). improbable. there must be thousands of cases in Irans.

In fact, there have been heated protests about the extreme pollution in Wuhan all throughout the year 2019 prior to this outbreak. People have been reporting a foul smell; children getting sick; respiratory illness (what they are trying to blame on coronavirus).  One of the pollution protests' biggest leaders was thrown into jail last year (2019), in typical communist Chinese fashion. We believe stories coming from China. The Chinese government even put out a press release stating “No foreign protesters are allowed to travel to Wuhan”.  In case you didn’t know Wuhan is an economic powerhouse; most of the top Fortune 500 businesses have factories there; it is at the level of Hong Kong when it comes to the Chinese economy.  Now I'm starting to wonder if they cooked this story to lock the city down in order to "round up" and or exterminate the protesters. Well, that was the initial reason, but I think due to the public scare “they” might now try to capitalize on the Coronavirus scare……IMHO

Sorry! China has done all they can do. We now have to repent of our sins and turn to the true living God of the bible who created all things and rested on the 7th day. Revelation 14:6-12 (KJV) And I saw another angel fly in the midst of heaven, having the everlasting gospel to preach unto them that dwell on the earth, and to every nation, and kindred, and tongue, and people,
Saying with a loud voice, Fear God, and give glory to him; for the hour of his judgment is come: and worship him that made heaven, and earth, and the sea, and the fountains of waters.
And there followed another angel, saying, Babylon is fallen, is fallen, that great city, because she made all nations drink of the wine of the wrath of her fornication.
And the third angel followed them, saying with a loud voice, If any man worship the beast and his image, and receive his mark in his forehead, or in his hand,
The same shall drink of the wine of the wrath of God, which is poured out without mixture into the cup of his indignation; and he shall be tormented with fire and brimstone in the presence of the holy angels, and in the presence of the Lamb:
And the smoke of their torment ascendeth up for ever and ever: and they have no rest day nor night, who worship the beast and his image, and whosoever receiveth the mark of his name.
Here is the patience of the saints: here are they that keep the commandments of God, and the faith of Jesus.🙏🏽
